Package: duke
Title: Makes color blind friendly visualizations with Duke's official colors
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Aidan", "Gildea", , "aidan.gildea@duke.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: The aim of this package is to allow for users to create Duke official visualizations in a color blind friendly way. By doing so, we can ensure that visualizations within our community are accessible to everyone.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.2.3
Imports: 
    ggplot2,
    scales,
    showtext,
    sysfonts,
    tibble
URL: https://github.com/aidangildea/duke,
    https://aidangildea.github.io/duke/
BugReports: https://github.com/aidangildea/duke/issues
Depends: 
    R (>= 2.10)
